## Limitations
This report primarily focuses on the negative aspects of labor unions as per the query. It does not delve into the positive impacts or the broader socio-economic benefits that unions may provide. Additionally, the findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives or the most recent data. Further research could provide a more balanced view of the role of labor unions in the economy.